#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/118509/ Hero id 118509 | Guide id
#: 697
msgid "The battlecruiser upgrades are very strong, but only starting from tavern 4. Don't invest too much into the upgrades early, then start buying some strong tavern 4 upgrades. At some point, you'll need to level to 6 for the reborn upgrade, which is absurdly OP. The best upgrade to buy is the deathrattle upgrade, and then you can multiply the enormous deathrattles with [[Titus Rivendare||97408]]."
msgstr "战列巡洋舰的升级非常强大，但只能从酒馆等级4开始。前期不要在升级上投入太多，然后从酒馆等级4开始购买一些强力的升级物品。在某些时候，你需要升到6级酒馆才能获得复生升级，这简直太超模了。最值得购买的升级是亡语升级，然后你可以用 [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] 来倍增强大的亡语加成。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/117409/ Hero id 117409 | Guide id
#: 695
msgid "Use this hero power like reno and use it on the first value generator you see, such as [[Bigwig Bandit||122179]]. If you don't find an early value generator, then use it on a core card for your direction."
msgstr "像雷诺一样用这个英雄技能，将其用于你看到的第一个资源生成器，例如[[Bigwig Bandit||122179]]。如果你没有在早期找到资源生成器，那就把它用在你的核心卡上。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/120649/ Hero id 120649 | Guide id
#: 701
msgid "Getting a value quest such as Pagle's Fishing Rod or Guiding Candle on Turn 8 is usually pretty sick, depending on your setup."
msgstr "在第8回合获得像帕格的鱼竿或引路蜡烛这样的价值饰品通常非常不错，具体效果取决于你的阵容。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/116926/ Hero id 116926 | Guide id
#: 694
msgid "This hero is very strong to copy the same, strong spell over and over. With an early [[Strike Oil||104029]], you can hero power every single turn to start printing Strike Oils. Then, later on you generate a strong spell such as [[Temperature Shift||117670]] every turn."
msgstr "这个英雄非常强，可以反复复制强力的法术。前期有[[Strike Oil||104029]]，你可以每回合都使用英雄技能复制钻探原油。到了后期你每回合都能生成一个强力法术，比如 [[Temperature Shift||117670]] 。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/120358/ Hero id 120358 | Guide id
#: 699
msgid "The Zerg provides guaranteed tempo, but might not stay in your comp. Level up your Zerg to tavern 2 when it costs only 0 or 1, because they are not that good. Tavern 3 Zergs are good though, but no need to rush it either. A lot of times you don't even level it to 3 and you have to sell the Zerg."
msgstr "异虫能提供稳定的节奏，但可能不会一直留在你的阵容中。当只要0或1铸币就能升级时再升级到酒馆2级，因为它们并不出色。不过酒馆3级的异虫还不错，但也没必要急于升级。很多时候你甚至不需要将异虫升级到3级就不得不卖掉它们。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/122925/ Hero id 122925 | Guide id
#: 702
msgid "Value summon cards such as [[Manasaber||98831]] or [[Icky Imp||74910]] because they'll give you more attacks so you can finish the hero power ASAP."
msgstr "优先使用 [[Manasaber||98831]] 或 [[Icky Imp||74910]] 等召唤卡牌，因为它们能为你提供更多攻击次数，让你能尽快触发英雄技能。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/117425/ Hero id 117425 | Guide id
#: 696
msgid "This hero power is mainly used to gain 1 gold per turn, similar to Murloc Holmes."
msgstr "这个英雄技能主要用来每回合获得1铸币，类似摩洛克·福尔摩斯。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/118510/ Hero id 118510 | Guide id
#: 698
msgid "Mothership is the best one to pick. Try to finish the hero power as soon as possible by buying everything that costs effectively 1 ([[Sellemental||64038]], [[Enchanted Lasso||104502]]). Make sure you buy summon units ([[Manasaber||98831]]) to farm 2+ protoss minions per turn."
msgstr "母舰是最好的选择。通过购买所有实际花费为1的物品([[Sellemental||64038]], [[Enchanted Lasso||104502]])来尽快解锁英雄技能。确保你购买了能召唤单位的随从 ([[Manasaber||98831]])，以便每回合养2+个星灵随从。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/116920/ Hero id 116920 | Guide id
#: 700
msgid "Always hero power the first 3 turns, freezing a 2 cost spell turn 1 if you can. Turn 4 onwards, you can choose to stop hero powering if buying a good minion is better. Definitely stop hero powering after turn 6 if you don't want to die."
msgstr "前3个回合一定要使用英雄技能，如果可以的话，在第1回合冻结一个2费法术。第4回合以后，如果买到一个好的随从，你可以选择停止使用英雄技能。如果你不想死，第6回合后一定要停止使用英雄技能。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/96870/ Hero id 96870 | Guide id
#: 381
msgid "This hero is not that good. Use it for slight earlygame tempo then forget about it."
msgstr "这个英雄没那么好。在游戏初期用它来打打节奏，然后就忘了它吧。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/99033/ Hero id 99033 | Guide id
#: 425
msgid "Copy for tempo turns 3 and 6, and copy to help whatever direction you're playing turn 9."
msgstr "在第3和第6回合复制抢节奏，然后在第9回合复制，以帮助你朝你想要方向前进。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/82110/ Hero id 82110 | Guide id
#: 213
msgid "This hero power is mainly to benefit avenge cards/trinkets such as [[Deathly Striker||115610]]."
msgstr "这个英雄技能主要有利于复仇的随从/饰品，比如 [[Deathly Striker||115610]]。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/86013/ Hero id 86013 | Guide id
#: 272
msgid "Your hero power will save some HP, otherwise play normally."
msgstr "你的英雄技能会帮你少掉点血，否则就正常玩。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/101345/ Hero id 101345 | Guide id
#: 424
msgid "Most of the time, go 3 on 3. Then, hero power on turns 4 and 5. The tier 3 buddies you're looking for are the value generating buddies, the one that gives you a minion every turn. There are quite a bit of them."
msgstr "大多数情况下，在第3回合升到3级酒馆。然后在第4和第5回合使用英雄技能。你要找的3级伙伴是那些能持续产生价值的伙伴，即每回合都能为你提供一个随从。这类伙伴的数量相当可观。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/61910/ Hero id 61910 | Guide id
#: 86
msgid "The more summons your board has, the more attacks will happen. Value cards that summon such as [[Manasaber||98831]] or [[Icky Imp||74910]] in the earlygame."
msgstr "你的棋盘上有越多的召唤物就会有越多的攻击次数。在早期游戏中要重视 [[Manasaber||98831]] 或 [[Icky Imp||74910]] 等召唤牌。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/98726/ Hero id 98726 | Guide id
#: 420
msgid "This hero is best used in Beast comps to target the [[Goldrinn, the Great Wolf||59955]] or Undead comps to target a reborn deathrattle undead ([[Friendly Giest]])."
msgstr "该英雄最适合在野兽流派中使用，以 [[Goldrinn, the Great Wolf||59955]] 为目标，或在亡灵流派中使用，以复生的亡语亡灵为目标（[[友善的恶鬼]])。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/101130/ Hero id 101130 | Guide id
#: 452
msgid "Buy most pirates in the early game to fill out your board fast so you can level and maybe play pirates but maybe play something else."
msgstr "在游戏初期尽可能多地购买海盗卡牌，快速填满你的棋盘，这样你就可以升级，也许可以玩海盗流派，但也可以玩其他的。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/89293/ Hero id 89293 | Guide id
#: 345
msgid "In the midgame, hero power when you have one gold left, but the hero power isn't good enough to play around."
msgstr "在游戏中期，当你还剩一铸币时，可以使用英雄技能，但英雄技能并不足以让你玩得尽兴。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/84867/ Hero id 84867 | Guide id
#: 322
msgid "After turn 1, keep track of everyone's tavern 1 unit! Murloc Holmes might have you choose between tier 1 units in the first few turns."
msgstr "第1回合后，记录每个人的酒馆1级随从！摩洛克·福尔摩斯可能会在前几个回合让你在1级随从中做出选择。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/97186/ Hero id 97186 | Guide id
#: 371
msgid "This hero power is not that good, just use it if you have one gold left in the midgame but don't play too hard into it."
msgstr "这个英雄技能并不是那么好，只要在游戏中期还剩一铸币时使用即可，但不要玩得太投入。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/103500/ Hero id 103500 | Guide id
#: 453
msgid "Play the game normally and use your hero power to save HP."
msgstr "正常玩游戏，使用英雄技能来减少掉血。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/86291/ Hero id 86291 | Guide id
#: 308
msgid "Most games your curve will be leveling to tavern 3 on turn 4, and then hero powering either your turn 5 shop or leveling. If you level on turn 5, then hero power your best tier 4 shop."
msgstr "大多数对局中你都会在第4回合提升到3级酒馆，然后在第5回合使用英雄技能或者升本。如果你在第5回合升本，那么就用技能买下最好的4级酒馆。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/68129/ Hero id 68129 | Guide id
#: 35
msgid "This hero is a bit slow, so use your hero power to discover a 5 drop for tempo. After you've stabilized, start printing 6 drops and win from there."
msgstr "这个英雄的节奏有点慢，所以为了抢节奏用你的英雄技能发现一个5级随从。稳定后开始发现6级随从，并从那里取胜。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/103477/ Hero id 103477 | Guide id
#: 504
msgid "[[Moira Bronzebeard||103502]] and [[King Varian||102998]] are generally the best 7 drops to pick because they're flexible. Naga's and Demon's 7 drop are pretty good too. Beast's 7 drop is only good with a [[Manasaber||98831]] turn 1."
msgstr "[[Moira Bronzebeard||103502]] 和 [[King Varian||102998]] 通常是最佳的 7 级卡牌选择，因为它们具有较高的灵活性。纳迦和恶魔的 7 级卡牌也相当不错。野兽的 7 级卡牌仅在第1回合搭配 [[Manasaber||98831]] 时效果较好。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/79719/ Hero id 79719 | Guide id
#: 166
msgid "Brukan's most common hero power is Lightning invocation, which is great to pop Divine Shields on your opponent's board. Brukan's summons can also be used to help with Quests and avenge cards."
msgstr "布鲁坎最常选的英雄技能是“闪电祈咒”，这非常适合在对手的场地上破圣盾。布鲁坎的召唤技能还可以用于完成任务和复仇。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/60211/ Hero id 60211 | Guide id
#: 122
msgid "The less armor a hero starts off with, the better pick it'll be with Finley. Snake Eyes starts with 6 armor, but if you pick it with Finley then you gain some extra armor with a good hero power."
msgstr "英雄的起始护甲越低，就越适合与芬利搭配。蛇眼的起始护甲是6，但如果与芬利搭配，就能获得额外的护甲和不错的英雄技能。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57924/ Hero id 57924 | Guide id
#: 25
msgid "Patchwerk 2.0, use hero power to preserve HP and don't play too hard into it."
msgstr "帕奇维克 2.0，使用英雄技能来保持生命值，不要过于依赖它。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/97813/ Hero id 97813 | Guide id
#: 402
msgid "Do not hero power on tavern 2 because tavern 2 creations are terrible. Instead, hero power on tavern 3 or tavern 4 and go for coin + reborn creations."
msgstr "不要在2级酒馆使用英雄技能，因为2级酒馆的亡灵作品非常糟糕。相反，在3级或4级酒馆使用英雄技能，并选择提供铸币+复生的亡灵作品。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/92960/ Hero id 92960 | Guide id
#: 324
msgid "Most of the time, the quest that you can complete the fastest and easiest is the best choice. For example, a summon quest with a [[Manasaber||98831]] opener is premium, but without any summons it's pretty bad."
msgstr "大多数时候，能最快最简单地完成的任务就是最好的选择。例如有 [[魔刃豹||98831]] 开局的召唤任务是很好的，但没有任何召唤物的话就糟了。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/58027/ Hero id 58027 | Guide id
#: 114
msgid "Try to lean into a [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] comp with this hero, such as Elemental or Murlocs, so you can keep a [[Tavern Tempest||64077]] or [[Magicfin's Apprentice]] on your board and proc it every turn."
msgstr "尝试用与 [[布莱恩·铜须||96786]] 搭配的流派使用这位英雄，例如元素或鱼人，这样你就可以在场上留一个 [[酒馆旋风||64077]] 或 [[魔鳍学徒]]，并在每回合触发其效果。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57944/ Hero id 57944 | Guide id
#: 27
msgid "If you find a 2 cost spell in your first two shops, you want to freeze it until turn 3. On turn 3, you can discover both your 3 drops and buy the 2 cost spell and level. The best 3 drops are the one that generate value every turn, such as [[Bigwig Bandit||122179]] or [[Greedy Snaketongue||122213]]"
msgstr "如果你在前两回合的酒馆中看到了一个2费法术，你应该把它冻结到第3回合。在第3回合，你可以发现你的3级随从并购买2费法术和提升酒馆等级。最好的3级随从是每回合都能产生资源的随从，例如 [[顶尖大盗||122179]] 或 [[贪婪的蛇信纳迦||122213]]"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/74646/ Hero id 74646 | Guide id
#: 150
msgid "Generally you keep a high attack low HP unit with this hero and give your warband lots of attack. The spellcrafts from Nagas are especially useful to \"control\" what your lowest HP unit is."
msgstr "一般来说，你可以为这个英雄保留一个高攻击低生命值的随从，并为你的阵容提供大量攻击力。纳迦的塑造法术在“控制”你的生命值最低的随从时尤其有用。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/60214/ Hero id 60214 | Guide id
#: 125
msgid "Typically, Murlocs and Elementals can utilize Brann the best, so try to have those tribes in as possible."
msgstr "通常，鱼人和元素可以最好地利用布莱恩·铜须，因此尽量选这些种族类型。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/105431/ Hero id 105431 | Guide id
#: 600
msgid "Don't expect much value from this hero power, it's basically Patchwerk 2.0."
msgstr "别指望这个英雄技能能带来多少价值，它基本上就是帕奇维克 2.0。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/60370/ Hero id 60370 | Guide id
#: 54
msgid "Force dragons on this hero, and use start of combat dragons such as [[Prized Promodrake||72073]] and [[Persistent Poet||108463]] to scale in the midgame."
msgstr "这个英雄强制使用龙，并在游戏中期使用 [[珍稀增强幼龙||72073]] 和 [[执念诗心龙||108463]] 等在战斗开始时获得属性来扩大龙的身材。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/61488/ Hero id 61488 | Guide id
#: 39
msgid "You must level to 4 on turn 5 on this hero! Either level to tavern 3 on turn 3 or turn 4 and then level to 4 on turn 5. Start hero powering every turn starting from turn 5. Even though you may start the game at low HP, you have to start getting your dragons up early on."
msgstr "你必须在第5回合就将酒馆等级提升至4级！要么在第3回合或第4回合将酒馆等级提升至3级，然后在第5回合将酒馆等级提升至4级。从第5回合开始，每回合都使用英雄技能。尽管游戏开始时你的生命值可能较低，但你必须尽早开始提升你的龙。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/60369/ Hero id 60369 | Guide id
#: 38
msgid "Only pick with Mechs in. Divine Shielded units such as [[Cord Puller||110101]] are premium in the early game. If you find no Divine Shields, then value units with higher HP."
msgstr "只选择机械圣盾随从，如 [[拔线机||110101]]，这在游戏初期非常重要。如果你没有发现圣盾，那么就要着重选择生命值较高的随从。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/105314/ Hero id 105314 | Guide id
#: 658
msgid "If you roll a 1 on turn 1, do NOT hero power on turn 2. Other than that, hero power whenever it's available."
msgstr "如果在第1回合投出1，就不要在第2回合发动英雄技能。除此以外，当英雄技能可用时立即使用。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/105434/ Hero id 105434 | Guide id
#: 604
msgid "You don't have to hero power every turn, only when you have 1 gold left over. For example, turn 2 you should still just level and not hero power."
msgstr "你不必每回合都使用英雄技能，只有当你剩1铸币时才使用。例如在第2回合，你仍然只需要升级酒馆，而不需要用英雄技能。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/62268/ Hero id 62268 | Guide id
#: 50
msgid "Use your hero power when it means finishing the quest a turn earlier. For example, if your quest is to play X battlecries and you can hero power to finish the quest, do it."
msgstr "当使用英雄技能意味着你能提前一回合完成任务时请务必使用。例如你的任务是触发X次战吼效果，而你可以通过使用英雄技能来完成任务，那么就立即使用。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/60362/ Hero id 60362 | Guide id
#: 127
msgid "Try to hero power turns 2-4 if you can. You can usually achieve this most efficiently by leveling to tavern 2 on turn 3. After that, hero power whenever you have 1 gold left, and don't feel like you have to press it."
msgstr "尽量在2到4回合内使用英雄技能。通常最有效的方法是在第3回合将酒馆等级提升至2级。之后只有剩余1铸币时再使用英雄技能，无需强行使用。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/64403/ Hero id 64403 | Guide id 5
msgid "Rally units are really nice with this hero power to attack twice with them."
msgstr "使用这个英雄技能时，进击单位可以进行两次攻击，效果非常不错。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/75702/ Hero id 75702 | Guide id
#: 16
msgid "Always go 3-2-3-2 flightpath while going tavern 3 on turn 3."
msgstr "总是选择 3-2-3-2 航线，在第3回合升到3级酒馆。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/62242/ Hero id 62242 | Guide id
#: 48
msgid "With Eudora, hero power every single turn starting from turn 1. This is done by leveling to tavern 2 on turn 3 and leveling to tavern 3 on turn 4. Your first hero power reward should be completed on tavern 3, turn 4. Use your second hero power reward on turn 8, and then stop hero powering from turn 9 onwards."
msgstr "使用尤朵拉时，从第1回合开始每回合都要使用英雄技能。具体做法是在第3回合将酒馆等级提升到2级，在第4回合将酒馆等级提升到3级。你的第一个英雄技能奖励应该在第4回合的3级酒馆完成。在第8回合获得第二个英雄技能奖励，然后从第9回合开始停止使用英雄技能。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/85125/ Hero id 85125 | Guide id
#: 293
msgid "This hero is mainly used to get permanent Divine shield with the [[Glowscale||80746]] spellcraft, aka worse George."
msgstr "这个英雄主要用 [[闪鳞纳迦||80746]] 来获得永久圣盾，又称更糟糕的乔治。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/64480/ Hero id 64480 | Guide id
#: 11
msgid "A ticket is roughly worth 1 gold, so any 1 cost spell with a ticket is worth buying. However, don't buy useless units for the sake of buying a ticket."
msgstr "一张暗月奖券大约价值1铸币，因此任何带有暗月奖券的1费法术都值得购买。但是也不要为了买暗月奖券而买无用的随从。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/113310/ Hero id 113310 | Guide id
#: 683
msgid "Don't be sad to choose Neutral lesser trinkets such as Well Oiled Can, they're all generally decent."
msgstr "选到中性的小饰品也不要伤心，如 “调酒机器人的油壶”，它们一般都很不错。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/79618/ Hero id 79618 | Guide id
#: 252
msgid "It's worth buying the highest attack units in your shop and pointy arrows to complete your quest ASAP. You ideally want this quest done turn 6 the latest. Then, start leveling and force a Naga comp."
msgstr "建议在商店中购买攻击力最高的单位和尖利箭矢，以尽快完成任务。理想情况下，应在第6回合前完成该任务。随后，开始升级并组建纳迦流派。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/58535/ Hero id 58535 | Guide id
#: 12
msgid "Patchwerk 2.0, only press this hero power if you don't have a better way to spend 2 gold, such as maybe on turn 3."
msgstr "帕奇维克 2.0，只有在你没有更好的方式来花费 2 铸币时，才使用这个英雄技能，比如在第3回合。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/62266/ Hero id 62266 | Guide id
#: 49
msgid "ONLY PICKABLE WITH BEASTS! Hero power 1 drops the first few turns and try to discover [[Southsea busker||98501]], [[Ominous Seer||117553]], or [[Alleycat||96758]]. Then, you can hero power the battlecry minion again and try to discover more battlecries."
msgstr "只在野兽局才选！在前几个回合对1级随从使用英雄技能并尝试发现 [[南海卖艺者||98501]], [[厄运先知||117553]], 或 [[雄斑虎||96758]]。然后你就可以再次对战吼随从使用英雄技能，并尝试发现更多战吼。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57634/ Hero id 57634 | Guide id
#: 109
msgid "Illidan is great with Rally cards because attacking first with them is quite important. It also allows for you to proc important rallys twice."
msgstr "伊利丹非常适合使用进击卡，因为用它们先手攻击非常重要。这还能让你触发重要的进击效果两次。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/63604/ Hero id 63604 | Guide id 3
msgid "Always think about your next turn! On turn 1, freeze a 2 cost spell or buy a [[Southsea Busker||98501]] so your turn 2 is much cleaner."
msgstr "时刻思考着你的下一回合！在第1回合，冻结一个2费法术或购买一个[[南海卖艺者||98501]]，这样你的第2回合就会流畅得多。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/59806/ Hero id 59806 | Guide id
#: 118
msgid "Use your hero power for early game tempo, saving HP and allowing you to level aggressively."
msgstr "在游戏初期使用英雄技能来获得游戏节奏，节省血量并让你能够积极地提升酒馆等级。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/60213/ Hero id 60213 | Guide id
#: 124
msgid "Hero power when it works out goldwise. For example, on turn 4 you may level to tavern 3 and hero power for 1. When your hero power costs 5, stop hero powering."
msgstr "在铸币充足的情况下使用英雄技能。例如，在第4回合，你可以升到3级酒馆并用1铸币使用英雄技能。当英雄技能耗费5铸币时，停止使用英雄技能。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/61914/ Hero id 61914 | Guide id
#: 47
msgid "Early game, your hero power is used to buy minions for 1 gold. Late game, you can hero power 5 drop and 6 drop spells in your shop to \"buy\" them for cheap."
msgstr "在游戏初期，你的英雄技能可以用来以1铸币的价格购买随从。在游戏后期，你可以使用英雄技能以低价“购买”5级和6级酒馆法术。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/73940/ Hero id 73940 | Guide id
#: 87
msgid "Patchwerk 2.0, only hero power if you don't have a better way to spend 1 gold."
msgstr "帕奇维克 2.0，如果你没有更好的方式来花费1铸币那么就用你的英雄技能。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/80239/ Hero id 80239 | Guide id
#: 167
msgid "Early game summons such as [[Manasaber||98831]] synergize well with the hero power. Then, you can put Divine Shielded units in the back such as [[Deflect-o-bot||61930]] to give you lots of midgame tempo."
msgstr "游戏初期的召唤物随从如 [[魔刃豹||98831]] 可以很好地与英雄技能协同。然后你可以在后排放置圣盾随从，如[[偏折机器人||61930]]，为你在游戏中期提供大量的节奏。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/61490/ Hero id 61490 | Guide id
#: 41
msgid "BEST PLAYED WITH BEASTS! Early game, after you play a Battlecry unit such as [[Alleycat||96758]] or [[Southsea Busker||98501]], hero power it to reroll it into something better. Lategame, you can use your hero power to reroll your 6 drops if you don't like them."
msgstr "最好玩野兽流派！在游戏初期，当你打出一个战吼随从（如[[Alleycat||96758]]或 [[Southsea Busker||98501]]）后，使用英雄技能将其替换为更好的随从。在游戏后期，如果你不喜欢你的6级随从，也可以使用英雄技能将其替换。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/80832/ Hero id 80832 | Guide id
#: 232
msgid "Even though you want to play Mechs eventually, Undead and Beasts provide the best early game summons so you can start having minions die early on."
msgstr "尽管你最终还是想玩机械流，但亡灵和野兽提供了最好的游戏前期召唤物，因此你可以在游戏初期就更多让随从死亡。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57635/ Hero id 57635 | Guide id
#: 110
msgid "Early game, hero power and freeze every turn, including turn 1, until you hit something you like from a higher tier. Never buy your 3 drop or 4 drop. 5 drops aren't that good this meta to buy, so freeze and next turn buy your best 6 drop. Value generating 6 drops are the best, such as [[Ignition Specialist||105852]] or [[Holo Rover||115674]]"
msgstr "在游戏初期，每回合（包括第1回合）都要使用英雄技能并冻结，直到你从更高的等级中找到你喜欢的东西。永远不要买你的3级或4级随从。5级随从在这个环境中并不值得购买，因此建议先保留，等到下回合再购买最佳的6级随从。能够产生资源的6级随从是最佳选择，例如 [[Ignition Specialist||105852]] 或 [[Holo Rover||115674]]"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/76521/ Hero id 76521 | Guide id
#: 143
msgid "The best way to use the hero power is to hero power your 6 drops lategame for utility and scam potential.  Other than that, hero powering is a bait."
msgstr "使用英雄技能的最佳方式是在后期对6级卡牌使用英雄技能，以获得实用性和欺骗潜力。除此之外，使用英雄技能只是一个诱饵。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/63601/ Hero id 63601 | Guide id 1
msgid "If you find an [[Alleycat||96758]] turn 1, swap it every turn (except turn 2 because it should be frozen in your shop), taking a 3 drop with your tabbycat triple turn 3 and taking a 5 drop on turn 6."
msgstr "如果你在第1回合找到了[[Alleycat||96758]]，每回合交换一次（除了第2回合，你应该把它冻结在商店里），在第3回合三连你的雌斑虎拿3级随从，在第6回合拿5级随从。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/59814/ Hero id 59814 | Guide id
#: 120
msgid "Use your bananas early game on a good unit to save HP in the earlygame and then play normally from there. If you don't find a good unit on turn 1, you should use all of them turn 3 the latest."
msgstr "在游戏初期将香蕉用在优质的随从上，以便在游戏初期节省血量，然后再正常游戏。如果第1回合没有找到好的随从，那么最迟在第3回合就应该使用所有的香蕉。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/61912/ Hero id 61912 | Guide id
#: 45
msgid "Get some free early buffs and after turn 7 the hero power becomes irrelevant so don't worry about it."
msgstr "获取一些免费的早期增益效果，到了第7回合后英雄技能就不再重要了，所以不用再想着技能了。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57893/ Hero id 57893 | Guide id
#: 111
msgid "Hero power the first 6 turns (except turn 2), and be tavern 4 by turn 6. Then, you don't have to hero power every turn, only when the tribe is useful to you."
msgstr "前6个回合（除了第2回合）都使用英雄技能，到第6回合升到4级酒馆。之后你就不必每回合都使用英雄技能了，只有当种族类型对你有用时才使用。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/64475/ Hero id 64475 | Guide id 6
msgid "Try not to spend a lot of money leveling on this hero. You can buy elementals, and then level to taverns 4, 5 or 6 when it's 2 or less gold."
msgstr "尽量不要在这个英雄身上花很多钱升级。你可以一直购买元素，然后在升级只要2或2以下铸币时升到4、5或6级酒馆。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/60366/ Hero id 60366 | Guide id
#: 129
msgid "You MUST play a cycle comp on this hero such as APM Pirates or Elementals - NOT Undeads, Beast, or Mechs!"
msgstr "这个英雄一定要玩循环流派！比如倒转海盗或元素。- 不要玩亡灵、野兽或机械！"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/59831/ Hero id 59831 | Guide id
#: 121
msgid "The only purpose of this hero is to save HP early game, so start hero powering every turn when the hero power reads +4 or +5 HP."
msgstr "这个英雄唯一的作用就是在游戏前期节省血量，所以当英雄技能描述上看到+4或+5生命值时就开始每回合使用英雄技能。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/66196/ Hero id 66196 | Guide id
#: 13
msgid "Hero power until turn 6 (except when you level on turn 2), and generally stop hero powering after that."
msgstr "在第6回合前都使用英雄技能（第2回合升级时除外），之后一般不再使用英雄技能。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/58534/ Hero id 58534 | Guide id
#: 30
msgid "The most common curve with this hero is to level hero power on turn 4, so turn 5 you can buy 2 good 4 drops, and play the game from there."
msgstr "这个英雄最常见的曲线是在第4回合升级，在第5回合你就可以买到2个不错的4级随从，然后从此开始游戏。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57892/ Hero id 57892 | Guide id
#: 24
msgid "Patchwerk 2.0, hero power gives you free stats in the midgame but don't play hard into it."
msgstr "帕奇维克 2.0，英雄技能在中后期为你提供免费属性加成，但不要过于依赖它。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/58435/ Hero id 58435 | Guide id
#: 29
msgid "The first 2 turns, freeze the entire shop to get buffed 1 drops. The following turns, buy your buffed 1 drops to make you strong in the early game. After turn 5, stop freezing the entire shop for the stats and just use your hero power to freeze a specific minion or spell."
msgstr "前2个回合，冻结整个商店，以获得Buff过的1级随从。在接下来的回合中，购买你Buff过的1级随从，让你在游戏前期变得更强。第5个回合后，停止为了获得属性而冻结整个商店，只需用英雄技能冻结特定的随从或法术。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/71463/ Hero id 71463 | Guide id
#: 22
msgid "If you plan on eating the entire shop, swap your largest attack unit into the shop first so you can turn your hero power attack into permanent attack. [[Channel the Devourer||100899]] and [[Mounting Avalanche||122862]] are other ways to turn temporary stats from your hero power into permanant stats."
msgstr "如果你打算吃掉整个商店，那就先把你攻击力最大随从换到商店里，这样你就可以把英雄技能的攻击力变成永久攻击力。 [[Channel the Devourer||100899]] 和 [[Mounting Avalanche||122862]] 是另一种将英雄技能的临时属性转化为永久属性的方法。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/64400/ Hero id 64400 | Guide id 4
msgid "You don't have to hero power every turn, just hero power when you have one gold left over, and make a big unit."
msgstr "你不必每回合都使用英雄技能，只需在剩余一铸币时使用英雄技能，造一个大随从。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57633/ Hero id 57633 | Guide id
#: 108
msgid "The hero power isn't that good, so only use it when you have one gold left over and don't play into too much."
msgstr "这个英雄的技能并没那么好，所以只有当你还剩一铸币时才使用它，而且不要玩得太投入。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/58021/ Hero id 58021 | Guide id
#: 112
msgid "If you have a deathrattle you really want to copy, then taunt it and choose Pack Tactics. Otherwise, usually choose Venomstrike Trap."
msgstr "如果你有一个非常想复制的亡语，那么让它获得嘲讽并选择集群战术。否则通常选择眼镜蛇陷阱。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/70838/ Hero id 70838 | Guide id
#: 210
msgid "Patchwerk 2.0, play the game normally and hero will passively preserve some HP."
msgstr "帕奇维克 2.0，正常玩游戏，这英雄会被动地保留一些生命值。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/67356/ Hero id 67356 | Guide id
#: 17
msgid "The best tier 1 spells are 2 coins or 3 refreshes. The best tier 2 spells are generally Great Deal and On the House."
msgstr "最好的1级法术是2个铸币或3次刷新。最好的2级法术一般是 “绝妙的交易 ”和 “免费酬宾”。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57891/ Hero id 57891 | Guide id
#: 23
msgid "In the early game, buy every [[Tad||87060]] and [[Patient Scout||97604]] as they generate you money. In the lategame, Gallywix relies on [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] to cycle lots of cards to ramp up economy. You must play a cycle composition with this hero, so try not to go Beasts or Undeads."
msgstr "在游戏前期，购买每一张 [[塔德||87060]] 和 [[耐心的侦查员||97604]]，因为它们能为你带来经济。在游戏后期，加里维克斯依靠 [[布莱恩·铜须||96786]] 循环使用大量卡牌来增加经济。你必须用这个英雄玩循环流派，所以尽量不要用野兽或亡灵。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/77516/ Hero id 77516 | Guide id
#: 142
msgid "Usually go 3 on 3 on this hero. In your first 3 turns, try to hero power the same tribe to maximize your chances of getting a higher tavern tier card. If you hero power all different tribes, you have the possibility of only discovering 1 drops from your hero power."
msgstr "通常在第3回合升到3级酒馆。在前3个回合中，尽量对同一个种族类型使用英雄技能，以最大限度地提高获得较高酒馆等级卡牌的机会。如果你对所有不同的种族类型使用英雄技能，你有可能只能从你的英雄技能中发现1级随从。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/81569/ Hero id 81569 | Guide id
#: 222
msgid "Very often the curve on this hero is to level to tavern 3 on turn 4 and level to 4 on turn 5 so you can unlock your 4 drop as soon as possible. The best 4 drops to pick are the ones that generate value every turn such as [[Lost City Looter||122175]]."
msgstr "这个英雄的曲线通常是在第4回合升到3级酒馆，然后在第5回合升到4级，这样就能尽快解锁4级随从。最好选择每回合都能产生经济的4级随从，例如 [[Lost City Looter||122175]]。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57929/ Hero id 57929 | Guide id
#: 26
msgid "Avoid using hero power on non permanent units, especially in the early game! The strength of this hero is its lategame, but your first priority is to find a direction first, and then you can hero power units part of that comp. George is actually quite good with Stegodon comp because you can divine shield windfury beasts."
msgstr "避免对不会留下来的随从使用英雄技能，尤其是在游戏前期！这个英雄的优势在于它的后期，但你的首要任务是先找到一个方向，然后你就可以对这个流派的部分随从使用英雄技能了。乔治其实相当擅长使用剑龙流派，因为你可以给风怒的野兽贴圣盾。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/60367/ Hero id 60367 | Guide id
#: 10
msgid "The more imbalanced the meta is, the better tess is, because everyone will just force a comp and you can steal it."
msgstr "环境越不平衡苔丝就越强，因为每个人都会被逼着玩同一个流派，而你可以偷它们。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/60372/ Hero id 60372 | Guide id
#: 42
msgid "Flurgl is best in an economy-centric lobby, because the hero power benefits from cycling cards. Even though you're a Murloc hero, pirate or elemental cycle comps utilizing [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] can make a ton of use out of your hero power."
msgstr "弗洛格尔最适合在以经济为中心的对局中使用，因为你的英雄技能可以从循环卡牌中获益。虽然你是个鱼人英雄，但利用 [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] 的海盗或元素循环流派也可以让你的英雄技能发挥巨大作用。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/63319/ Hero id 63319 | Guide id
#: 52
msgid "You have a lot of armor to work with, so don't be scared of leveling fast. You're basically Patchwerk with less HP, but higher chance to win the lobby."
msgstr "你有大量护甲可以使用，所以不要怕快速升级。你基本上就是一个生命值较低的帕奇维克，但在酒馆中获胜的几率更高。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/58044/ Hero id 58044 | Guide id
#: 115
msgid "Definitely hero power + buy on turn 1, level on turn 2, and hero power + buy on turn 3. You don't have to hero power after that unless you really need the gold."
msgstr "绝对要在第1回合使用英雄技能购买随从，第2回合升级，第3回合再次使用英雄技能购买。之后无需再使用英雄技能，除非你真的需要金币。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/59203/ Hero id 59203 | Guide id
#: 33
msgid "You can reborn the Amalgam using [[Drakkari Embalmer||99121]] or [[Sprightly Scarab||108909]], and then Divine Shield the Amalgam using [[Annoy-o-module||96812]]."
msgstr "你可以使用 [[Drakkari Embalmer||99121]] 或 [[Sprightly Scarab||108909]] 让融合怪获得复生，然后使用 [[Annoy-o-module||96812]] 为融合怪施加圣盾。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57947/ Hero id 57947 | Guide id
#: 44
msgid "Buy every pirate in the early game. Hero powering is also usually better than buying a non-pirate card."
msgstr "在游戏初期买下每一个海盗。直接使用英雄技能通常也比购买非海盗随从要好。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/66483/ Hero id 66483 | Guide id
#: 14
msgid "Beasts and Undead compositions are the best for fish, although don't be afraid to use it for tempo and discard it later."
msgstr "野兽和亡灵的流派最适合养鱼，不过也别怕用它来打节奏，之后再把它卖掉。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/57946/ Hero id 57946 | Guide id
#: 28
msgid "Buy some Mechs early game for tempo, and then forget about the hero power because it is not impactful midgame and lategame."
msgstr "在游戏初期买一些机械来打节奏，然后忘掉你的英雄技能，因为它在游戏中期和后期没有影响。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/74631/ Hero id 74631 | Guide id
#: 37
msgid "Don't worry about the hero power too early. In most cases, use your first hero power proc after you level to tavern 3. [[Freedealing Gambler||61049]] is a must buy to get potential free hero power procs."
msgstr "不要过早担心英雄技能。在大多数情况下，建议在升级到酒馆3级后再使用你的第一个英雄技能触发效果。[[Freedealing Gambler||61049]] 是必买的卡牌，可以获得潜在的免费英雄技能触发效果。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/59807/ Hero id 59807 | Guide id
#: 119
msgid "Only use the hero power if you have one gold left over, this hero power isn't good enough even if you're playing demons."
msgstr "只有当你还剩下一铸币时才会使用英雄力量，即使你在玩恶魔流派这种英雄技能也不够好。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/61489/ Hero id 61489 | Guide id
#: 40
msgid "Turn 1 if you have a 2 cost spell in your first shop, buy it and then roll and you'll likely roll into a 1 cost spell that you can then buy. Same thing with coin, buy it and roll and hope to get a 2 cost spell in your next shop."
msgstr "第1回合，如果你的第一个商店里有一个2费法术，买下它然后刷新，你很可能会刷到一个1费法术，然后再买下它。硬币也是一样，买下它然后刷新，希望能在下一个商店里获得2费法术。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/71454/ Hero id 71454 | Guide id
#: 19
msgid "The best way to use the hero power is to use it on Magnetics in the shop to attach it onto good Mechs."
msgstr "使用英雄技能的最佳方法是将其用于商店中的磁力随从，再将其吸附在优秀的机械上。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/76562/ Hero id 76562 | Guide id
#: 172
msgid "This hero is best in metas where you can steal heroes' pets (such as Fish of Nzoth). Right now, you don't see a lot of those though."
msgstr "这个英雄在可以偷取英雄的伙伴（比如恩佐斯的鱼）的环境里是最强的。不过现在这种情况并不多见。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/80247/ Hero id 80247 | Guide id
#: 168
msgid "Early game summons such as [[Icky Imp||74910]] are really good for the hero power. Use that tempo to save HP, level, and search for a lategame direction."
msgstr "游戏初期的召唤物，如 [[Icky Imp||74910]] ，对英雄技能非常有利。利用这种节奏来节省血量、提升等级并寻找游戏后期的方向。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/71908/ Hero id 71908 | Guide id
#: 51
msgid "Did you know OP hero powers such as Reno or Zerek appear less frequently?"
msgstr "你知道雷诺或泽里克等超模的英雄技能的出现率较低吗？"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/71458/ Hero id 71458 | Guide id
#: 21
msgid "Your hero power acts as gem generation, so commit to quilboars the moment you find [[Prickly Piper||98946]] to scale your gems."
msgstr "你的英雄技能就像鲜血宝石生成器一样，所以在找到[[Prickly Piper||98946]]的那一刻就转入野猪人流派中，以增加你的鲜血宝石属性。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/71916/ Hero id 71916 | Guide id
#: 36
msgid "This hero can be fun with shop buff Elementals to consume them with your hero power."
msgstr "这个英雄玩商店Buff的元素流派非常有趣，用你的英雄技能吞噬它们。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/59397/ Hero id 59397 | Guide id
#: 34
msgid "You can afford to stabilize on higher tavern tiers because of your extra HP."
msgstr "由于你有额外的生命值，你可以在较高的酒馆等级上稳定下来。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/77987/ Hero id 77987 | Guide id
#: 165
msgid "In the early game, aim high to damage their strongest unit. In the lategame, aim low to snipe off scam cards such as [[Leeroy the Reckless||90425]]."
msgstr "在游戏初期选瞄准高处，伤害他们最强的单位。在游戏后期选瞄准低处，狙击[[Leeroy the Reckless||90425]]等陷阱卡。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/58024/ Hero id 58024 | Guide id
#: 113
msgid "In the endgame, running reborn [[Leeroy the Reckless||90425]] is very strong in general."
msgstr "在终局，复生的 [[Leeroy the Reckless||90425]] 一般来说非常强大。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/70956/ Hero id 70956 | Guide id
#: 20
msgid "Hero powering 1/1s and 1/2s in shop early on is great on this hero in the early game. Mid to late game just hero power good battlecries such as [[Rodeo Performer||104466]]."
msgstr "在游戏前期，对商店中的1/1和1/2们使用英雄技能非常有用。游戏中后期只需对不错的战吼随从使用英雄技能，如[[Rodeo Performer||104466]]。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/79615/ Hero id 79615 | Guide id
#: 212
msgid "If you roll into a frozen card you want to triple, you can leave it frozen to try to get a 3rd frozen copy in the shop next turn. For example, if your hero power copied a Brann, you can leave one or two Branns frozen in the shop, and the hero power might copy it again next turn."
msgstr "如果你刷到一张你想要三连的冻结卡牌，你可以让它处于冻结状态，争取下一回合在商店中获得第三张冻结的它。例如，如果你的英雄技能复制了一张布莱恩·铜须，你可以在商店里留下一到两张被冻结的布莱恩·铜须，下一回合英雄技能可能会再次复制它。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/63602/ Hero id 63602 | Guide id 2
msgid "To win your bets, generally bet against the person on higher tavern tier. In terms of using your coins, usually hold your coins to use on higher tavern tiers. Don't buy trash!"
msgstr "要想赢得赌注，一般要给酒馆等级较高的人下注。在使用铸币方面，通常要攒着铸币在较高的酒馆等级上使用。不要买垃圾！"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/67553/ Hero id 67553 | Guide id
#: 18
msgid "This hero is strong with token builds, notably Beast or Undead compositions. Try to lean towards those comps!"
msgstr "这个英雄在超生流派中很强，尤其是野兽或亡灵流。尽量向这些流派靠拢！"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/60212/ Hero id 60212 | Guide id
#: 123
msgid "Either golden an early value generator or the first directional card you see. Value generators such as turn 5 [[Bigwig Bandit||122179]] will give you so much value so you can level fast with a strong board. Directional cards include [[Sanguine Refiner||122566]] or [[Nomi, Kitchen Nightmare||63626]], and then you just commit to that direction."
msgstr "无论是点金早期资源生成器，还是你看到的第一个方向性卡牌。资源生成器例如第5回合的[[Bigwig Bandit||122179]]能为你提供大量资源，让你能快速升级并建立强大的场面。方向性卡牌包括 [[Sanguine Refiner||122566]] 或 [[Nomi, Kitchen Nightmare||63626]]，之后你只需专注于该方向即可。"

#: https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/heroes/64485/ Hero id 64485 | Guide id 9
msgid "Use your first hero power or two on early pairs to try to stabilize. You can use your last hero power on a core card for your direction, such as [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] or [[Titus Rivendare||97408]]."
msgstr "将你的第一个或两个英雄技能用在前期，尽量稳住局势。你可以将最后一次英雄技能用在你的核心卡牌上，例如 [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] 或 [[Titus Rivendare||97408]]。"

